{"tid":2077211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民黃兆健：《東周刊》頭版報道小弟「不務正業宣傳抗爭」，對於區務未跟進。亂世當中，請大家多珍惜、讚賞、唱好熱狗。","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:19:42.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b5fc9378a25c5700d09dafe83a03f7b34066fb","tid":2077211,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"黃兆健：<br />\n今期《東周刊》頭版報道小弟，指本人「不務正業宣傳抗爭」，對於區務如違泊問題卻未跟進。<br />\n重點：本人認為張相揀得幾好。感謝。<br />\n事實上，作為地區出身的政治人物，相信一眾朋友會認同熱狗的地區工作。本人團隊的地區工作，亦未因「宣傳抗爭」而停步，並謙卑地服務街坊。<br />\n過去數週街站，我們一直同街坊簡述，熱血公民在「反修例運動」至今的人道支援工作，包括 #熱血安全車隊、#熱血義診服務、#國民支援配對計劃。<br />\n亂世當中，請大家多珍惜、讚賞、唱好熱狗，並加入團隊幫忙。感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3DDG8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3DDG8D.jpg&h=8c418818&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2d8a4320783ae2cda828f3e26a518c780ee1da1","tid":2077211,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"PR公司就係用呢啲方法去令連登仔唔識思考<br />\n用一啲account去狂推唔同派別KOL嘅發言<br />\n選擇性咁借KOL把口去帶風向<br />\n斷章取義咁去捧神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp2g8iZ.png&amp;h=ac945bad&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6j3Ojq.png&amp;h=e6e2f7de&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHcdq6r.png&amp;h=b475b979&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"1e747508fb8d2b98f70f0b23dbd6c68e6e3d1d96","tid":2077211,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e5364fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"3c2dc95e2589c05e822f4a2492bd2e31656fa2cb","